prisma_schema:
generator client {
    provider      = "prisma-client-js"
    binaryTargets = ["native", "debian-openssl-1.1.x"]
}

datasource db {
    provider = "postgresql"
    url      = "postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/entity_store?schema=public"
}

model A1_CustomerPayments {
    record_id                             BigInt    @id
    CustomerName                          String?
    CustomerID                            String?
    ReceivablesCriteria                   String?
    ReceivablesCOA                        String?
    ReceivablesCOAID                      String?
    AmountReceived                        Decimal?  @db.Decimal
    PaymentDate                           DateTime? @db.Timestamp(6)
    PaymentNumber                         String?
    PaymentMode                           String?
    DepostiAccountcriteria                String?
    DepositTo                             String?
    DepositToCOAID                        String?
    Reference                             String?
    TaxDeducted                           String?
    TdsTaxAccount                         String?
    TdsTaxAccountCOAID                    String?
    TransactionReferenceNumber            String?
    AmountUsedForPayments                 Decimal?  @db.Decimal
    WithHoldingTaxPaid                    Decimal?  @db.Decimal
    BalanceDue                            Decimal?  @db.Decimal
    AmountInExcess                        Decimal?  @db.Decimal
    DoYouWantToRefundExcessAmountReceived String?
    AmountRefunded                        Decimal?  @db.Decimal
    NotifyCustomer                        String?
    NotificationMode                      String?
    NotificationMessage                   String?
    UserName                              String?
    UserMobileNumber                      String?
    UserEmail                             String?
    Attachments                           String?
    Notes                                 String?
    InstrumentRefNo                       String?
    DateOfReceipt                         DateTime? @db.Timestamp(6)
    SourceDetails                         String?
    parent_id                             BigInt?
    org_unit_id                           BigInt?
    owner_id                              BigInt?
    audit_data                            String?
    updated_at                            BigInt?

    @@index([parent_id], map: "parentid_16770701192952127839677")
    @@map("A1 dcdccd")
}
